snippet.title: Grandma Green - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as an adorable Grandma, bring talking plants to life, and cultivate the garden of your dreams!

Grandma Green is an upcoming, free-to-play, indie cozy gardening game coming to iOS and Android! Stay tuned for our official launch this May!

Pre-Order: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/grandma-green/id1633574120
